urface when: TOOL ROUTING - Search & Retrieval Decision Tree | Prioritize when: task context aligns with \\\"TOOL ROUTING - Search & Retrieval Decision Tree\\\"\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 9417,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/comment-hygiene.md\",\n          \"title\": \"Comment Hygiene — No Ephemeral Artifact Pointers in Code Comments\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — must be caught | Prioritize when: Never embed spec-folder paths, packet/phase numbers, ADR ids, task/checklist/requirement ids, or finding ids in code co…\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 9416,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/cli-dispatch-skill-preload.md\",\n          \"title\": \"CLI DISPATCH — Skill Preload Mandate\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — MUST `Read` `.opencode/skills/cli-X/SKILL.md` first.** | Prioritize when: global config default.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 9380,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/verify-before-completion-claims.md\",\n          \"title\": \"Verify Before Completion Claims\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: a positive check whose result you actually read. | Prioritize when: a state that isn't real. (Owner: \\\"Report outcomes faithfully\\\"; \\\"never claim an unverified commit/file.\\\")\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 9378,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/spec-folder-naming.md\",\n          \"title\": \"Spec-Folder Naming & Rename Convention\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — NEVER delete + recreate. | Prioritize when: never hand-edit (e.g. advisor `skill-graph.json` via `skill_graph_compiler.py --export-json`).\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 9376,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/post-implementation-deep-review.md\",\n          \"title\": \"POST-IMPLEMENTATION DEEP-REVIEW — Mandatory after substantive ship\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: asserting new invariant | | Prioritize when: asserting new invariant |\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 9375,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/memory-system-spec-kit-only.md\",\n          \"title\": \"MEMORY — Spec-Kit System Only\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — do not silently choose native. | Prioritize when: constitutional rule is active for current task\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 9374,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/memory-db-file-topology.md\",\n          \"title\": \"MEMORY — Spec-Kit DB File Topology (index vs vectors are SEPARATE files)\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: MEMORY — Spec-Kit DB File Topology (index vs vectors are SEPARATE files) | Prioritize when: task context aligns with \\\"MEMORY — Spec-Kit DB File Topology (index vs vectors are SEPARATE files)\\\"\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 9373,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/main-branch-direct-push.md\",\n          \"title\": \"Main Branch — Owner's AIs Push Directly\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — Do NOT default to a feature-branch + PR flow, do NOT re-ask whether to use a PR, and do NOT flag the bypass or the unsi… | Prioritize when: only (the tree often has concurrent parallel-session work + daemon metadata churn — NEVER `git add -A` blindly; use exp…\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 9372,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/gate-tool-routing.md\",\n          \"title\": \"TOOL ROUTING - Search & Retrieval Decision Tree\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: TOOL ROUTING - Search & Retrieval Decision Tree | Prioritize when: task context aligns with \\\"TOOL ROUTING - Search & Retrieval Decision Tree\\\"\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"triggered\": [\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 6891,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/049-system-analysis-bugs\",\n          \"title\": \"System-Spec-Kit Bug [system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/049-system-analysis-bugs/spec]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"system\",\n            \"spec\",\n            \"kit\",\n            \"analysis\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 6831,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/042-post-merge-refinement-5\",\n          \"title\": \"Spec Kit [system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/042-post-merge-refinement-5/decision-record]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"spec\",\n            \"kit\",\n            \"memory\",\n            \"system\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 6742,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/027-memory-plugin-and-refinement/001-memory-repo-analysis\",\n          \"title\": \"...spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/027-memory-plugin-and-refinement/001-memory-repo-analysis/spec]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"memory\",\n            \"system\",\n            \"analysis\",\n            \"spec\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 6818,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/042-post-merge-refinement-5\",\n          \"title\": \"Tasks: Spec Kit [system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/042-post-merge-refinement-5/tasks]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"spec\",\n            \"kit\",\n            \"memory\",\n            \"system\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 8668,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/024-compact-code-graph/021-cross-runtime-instruction-parity\",\n          \"title\": \"Phase 021: Cross-Runtime [system-spec-kit/024-compact-code-graph/021-cross-runtime-instruction-parity/spec]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"cross\",\n            \"runtime\",\n            \"spec\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ],\n      \"surfaced_at\": \"2026-06-08T13:33:33.077Z\",\n      \"latencyMs\": 144\n    },\n    \"tokenBudget\": 3500\n  }\n}","metadata":{"truncated":false},"title":"","time":{"start":1780925612929,"end":1780925613081}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0495bf9f29074fae016a26c4ab59748191a42564b9fd94c01a"}},"id":"prt_ea7703d6c001EUOOeGcnCdcBT2","sessionID":"ses_158903c24ffeYh4HmE3B8vB3CW","messageID":"msg_ea7702cb60012qbaHrpTX5DGkf"}}
